Module  : Make Profiles Private
Version : 1.0.1
Author  : James Lehmann a.k.a. Ravenswood
Patches : Maurice Makaay

This module prevents people from seeing profiles unless they are logged in.


Installation instructions:
--------------------------

- Unpack the archive;

- Move the directory "make_profiles_private" to the directory "mods"
  within your Phorum installation;

- Login as administrator in Phorum's administrative interface and
  go to the "Modules" section;

- Enable the module "Make Profiles Private".

